    "body": "Thanks for a quick response. Sounds good.  I will add a few preliminary research I quickly done\r\n\r\n- EIP-1202 (#1202) will benefit from this proposal for *able to perform session-key encrypted `commit` vote in a PLCR situation*\r\n- EIP-1484(#1484), EIP-1775(#1775) etc will benefit from being able to create *derived (per-session) identity* \r\n\r\nOr in general, it allows Dapps to perform 1-way or 2-way handshakes by exchanging session-based keys for authentication or encryption purposes.\r\n\r\nOther potential benefited EIPs: EIP-1328(#1328), EIP-627( #1659), #1271\r\n\r\n**I don't think any existing EIP addresses the similar problem and its scope sounds reasonable**, I personal think this proposal is a good idea, and will be pleased to see a draft started.\r\n",
